title: DDFP 86: The day Rank took the reins
itunes:title: DDFP 86: The day Rank took the reins
description:
Episode 86 features Dave Dameshek from New York City, as he prepares for three days of the NFL Fantasy Live Show as part of NFL.com Fantasy Draft Week. Also joining the show are the Around the League fellas, Dan Hanzus and Mark Sessler, who participate in a new segment, “It’s a Quarterback League.” And Elliot Harrison rounds out this star-studded show as he sits in for “The Blue List” to talk Jon Gruden, Mike Scioscia and “Top Gun.” You’re gonna love it. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
